    <item>
      <title>Brookfield 表示其 PE 业务规模有望在五年内扩大三倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/brookfield-says-it-can-triple-size-of-pe-business-in-five-years-lx1nv1oe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁克菲尔德资产管理公司 (Brookfield Asset Management) 负责人阿努吉·兰詹 (Anuj Ranjan) 在接受彭博电视采访时表示，该公司可以在未来五年内将其私募股权部门的规模扩大两倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/brookfield-says-it-can-triple-size-of-pe-business-in-five-years-lx1nv1oe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 10:03:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗的 Badoy 认为，哪些欧洲股票在通胀上升的情况下表现良好？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-05/citi-s-badoy-european-equity-environment-changing-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗欧洲股票研究主管 Elise Badoy 表示，由于利率上升，投资者可能会看到欧洲股市未来环境有所不同。她在彭博电视的“Francine Lacqua 脉搏”节目中列举了该行的优先股板块。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-05/citi-s-badoy-european-equity-environment-changing-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 10:01:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
