      <title>莫迪的选举挫折对一些全球股票基金来说只是昙花一现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/modi-s-election-setback-only-a-blip-for-some-global-stock-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于许多外国投资者来说，印度股市周二暴跌近 4000 亿美元，这正是投资这个他们眼中全球最有前景的经济体之一的又一个机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/modi-s-election-setback-only-a-blip-for-some-global-stock-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 06:25:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鸽派利率押注推动股市上涨；债券市场涨势暂停：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场猜测经济降温将为美联储今年降息提供空间，股市因此上涨。美国国债止住了引发收益率今年最大两日跌幅的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 22:31:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易员纷纷押注美联储加快降息步伐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/bond-traders-pile-into-fresh-bets-on-faster-pace-of-fed-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员再次倾向于鸽派，随着国债价格上涨，他们加大押注，认为美联储加快降息步伐将使债券受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/bond-traders-pile-into-fresh-bets-on-faster-pace-of-fed-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 20:30:21 GMT</pubDate>
